But we have a lot of resources on the veniver.rstudio.com

00:47:20.879 --> 00:47:23.239
website if there are things that people

00:47:23.239 --> 00:47:26.959
are interested in learning about or want supported in Veniver.

00:47:26.959 --> 00:47:31.879
We're always taking requests if you want to open an issue.

00:47:31.879 --> 00:47:33.320
Links to the GitHub are on that site

00:47:33.320 --> 00:47:39.159
as well for both R or Python, or even any feedback you have.

00:47:39.159 --> 00:47:40.080
We're very welcoming.

00:47:40.479 --> 00:47:43.639
We want anyone who has thoughts or opinions on Veniver

00:47:43.639 --> 00:47:44.879
to chime in.

00:47:44.879 --> 00:47:48.520
It's an open source project to serve everyone,

00:47:48.520 --> 00:47:52.000
to really serve this community.

